OL,2,MFrom zero to engineering superhero
OL,4,CMat Zolnierczyk
OL,5,CSun 10:00-10:20
OL,6,CStage C
OL,8,GSix years ago, I was an artist with no
OL,9,Gengineering qualifications, no formal
OL,10,Gtechnical training, and absolutely no
OL,11,Gbusiness operating industrial robots
OL,12,Gworth hundreds of thousands of pounds.
OL,13,GToday, I lead robotics projects for
OL,14,Gcompanies around the world. This talk
OL,15,Gis a light-hearted cautionary tale of
OL,16,Ghow curiosity, persistence, and an
OL,17,Gunhealthy number of browser tabs
OL,18,Gcompletely changed the direction of my
OL,19,Glife. Through stories of failure,
OL,20,Gcareer detours, imposter syndrome,
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
